Call Flow Diagram

[Merchant Calls 1800-XXX-XXXX]
       ↓
[IVR: "Welcome to Paytm Business Travel"]
       ↓
[AI Agent Answers: "Namaste Ramesh bhai, kahan jaana hai?"]
       ↓ (15 sec)
[NLU Extracts: Origin, Destination, Date]
       ↓
[Flight Search API Call]
       ↓ (30 sec)
[Agent Reads 2 Options | WhatsApp Shows Cards]
       ↓
[Merchant Confirms: "Air India wala"]
       ↓ (45 sec)
[Payment Method: "Credit se" → ₹3,800 deducted]
       ↓
[Booking Confirmed → PNR Generated]
       ↓ (75 sec)
[GST Invoice Auto-Generated → WhatsApp PDF]
       ↓
[Agent Reads Summary | E-ticket Sent]
       ↓ (90 sec)
[Call Ends: "Safe travels!"]

